messages.subject: Peabody Conference
messages.msgSnippet: Hi All, We are still on a high from a truly amazing weekend. It was SO neat to look at unfamiliar faces and then check out a familiar name on a tag!! Let s see
messages.messageBody:
Hi All,

We are still on a high from a truly amazing weekend. It was SO neat
to look at unfamiliar faces and then check out a familiar name on a
tag!! Let's see if I can remember all.. It was just a delight to
meet you, Jann(et) ;), Robin, Laura, Kelly, Ben, Rue, Beth.. sheesh,
I know I'm forgetting someone.. sorry if I have!

Thank you, Ben, and the SSUDS group. It was EXACTLY what both my
husband and I needed to really jump in with both feet. My children
had a really fun time connecting with open, friendly, bright
children. It's not always easy to take my HS Christian places and
for him not to feel threatened in some way .. so I thank you.

And to Ren, HA! I floated under the radar but I was there and in
your presence often!! ;)

I just picked up a book today _The Unprocessed Child_ by Valerie
Fitzeneiter. It speaks to RU deeply.

I'm so proud of my children and being at a conference like the one
in Peabody just made me cherish them more.

Thank you, All,
Tonya
Proud Mama to
Christian 5-30-95 (happy birthday tomorrow XOX)
Rory 6-9-99 (energy to the nth degree)
Alannah 6-18-03 (my curly girl ;) )

Btw Jann, thanks for the email and recommendations. Off to the
Library tomorrow! :-)
